      "eng": "Tsk!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "chn": "真吝啬。",
      "jap": "しけてるねぇ",
      "eng": "Throw me a bone, will you?",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "chn": "你也撑不了多久啦，",
      "jap": "あんた、もう長くないぜ",
      "eng": "You haven't got much time anyway.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "chn": "对不对啊，尤莉亚？",
      "jap": "なあ、ユリア？",
      "eng": "Right, Yulia?",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "chn": "#0第3次未完成交易，互动列表-选择「离去」",
      "jap": "#0リストから選択:立ち去る(何もしなかった):C",
      "eng": "#0Menu-Choose \"Leave\" 3rd time without purchasing something",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "chn": "哼",
      "jap": "フン",
      "eng": "Hmph.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "chn": "怎么，消遗我啊？",
      "jap": "なんだ、ひやかしかよ",
      "eng": "What a waste of time.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "chn": "去死吧，垃圾。",
      "jap": "終わっちまえ、屑が",
      "eng": "Go and fall off a cliff. ",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
